      "writtenOn": "2018-11-29T23:39:31Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "don\u0027t use change_id here. Should be number instead. change_id isn\u0027t unique, even if you annotate it with project and target ref.\n\nIf you do it in this CL, then please also add optional project field. Gerrit appreciates when REST API specifies \"project~number\", because it provides for more efficient routing.",
      "revId": "a6615c41be2bae90aaaca1766325c6294be8b843",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba",
